name: Playboy Magazine October 2011 Issue
description:
Amanda Cerny is a playmate centerfold for the October 2011 issue of Playboy. This is the 1960s issue. A collectors edition!

You may notice the two options to either have the issue signed or signed and personalized. The personalized issue is a lesser price for you! When ordering a personalized signed issue, If you'd like, include the personalization instructions in the notes of the order otherwise it will be personalized to the name on the receipt .
